ActEmployment Insurance Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Employment Insurance (Fishing) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE (FISHING) REGULATIONS in order to (1) align the Fishing Regulations with the Employment Insurance Act and Employment Insurance Regulations; and (2) ensure that fishers who claim EI benefits are treated the same as other EI claimants.
